{"tid":2211541,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地係唔係連「中國」呢一個詞都唔應該使用？","createTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T18:04:08.000Z","uid":211994,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf81de224860f3613d28d6d0d9a5c5e6a2bcd46","tid":2211541,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"話說樓主去咗了解下南蒙古發生緊咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9uUw2IQMxaM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9uUw2IQMxaM&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZosemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=7e6b57f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9uUw2IQMxaM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">9:55</span>開始，主持人話「中國」呢一個詞，本身就包涵咗支那人認為佢地國家係「位於天下中心嘅一國」，<strong><span class=\"gold\">係從支那人嘅角度出發</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學習「中國」呢個詞彙嘅同時，亦都被灌輸咗「支那係世界中心，全地球圍住佢轉」嘅觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而喺南蒙古語中，「中國」呢個詞語，意思係「位於蒙古南方嘅契丹國」，<strong><span class=\"gold\">係從蒙古人嘅角度出發</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後主持人總結係<em>「不同語言背後，隱含嘅世界觀會是不一樣的」</em><br />\n<br />\n所以樓主就諗，我地係唔係要用其他叫法去稱呼鄰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5875a8367b7f6fd5d7915629c0773aebf7775ca","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4edfabc271dae8b3cdc6427e2d2eb8b3ea260c0d","tid":2211541,"uid":331739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"咁日本呢個名都係由中國出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08db97107f4ca84feb2e1dc911d8ec4226b98945","tid":2211541,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"其實唔同釋名真係可以有好多唔同意思<br />\n英文China即頭係講緊秦國添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4693f48a5b5d45e3f20dcdb751cb6e549bcd51a1","tid":2211541,"uid":377707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"支那 / 震旦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ba097ae2f802ed6158902b5979c9ecf44922a1","tid":2211541,"uid":312114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"震旦"},{"pid":"92270cf5d8ad165430bf7e6df853016e8d318206","tid":2211541,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T18:40:41.000Z","msg":"支那"},{"pid":"88cf6859f1ebf5fd6fba64d8cd93adaaf806a073","tid":2211541,"uid":138144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T19:59:58.000Z","msg":"啱 所以我一般都會用支那"},{"pid":"a94b3707c8ca0d071a5dc23f4a80737c5568f9c8","tid":2211541,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T20:34:36.000Z","msg":"用地理名詞？"},{"pid":"00ba872900fc3d0e0190430f93f8ae76f5954b30","tid":2211541,"uid":147198,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:13:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得連中文都唔應該用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66247bf7b450df625e7fcb1aad5fccc8ae091e09","tid":2211541,"uid":97389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T22:47:33.000Z","msg":"呢個我而家視為&ldquo;地理名詞&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n作為地理名詞，&ldquo;一個中國&rdquo;係冇任何問題的，因為呢個世界的確只有一個土地叫做&ldquo;China&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n但呢個名為China的地方到底有幾個個主權國家/主權政府存在，係應該基於該土地人民的自由意志。<br />\n<br />\n當然&rdquo;自由意志&ldquo;係有前題/假設：人民必需要同普世價值，自由，民主，人權，法治接軌，否則&rdquo;自由意志&ldquo;只會再成全世界的災禍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbddb761cd7cc4ed43a593cdbb55a35441ab9a1","tid":2211541,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b5875a8367b7f6fd5d7915629c0773aebf7775ca","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"當初會停用呢個字係因為1945年中華民國要求日本停用 <br />\n<br />\n不過到今日都支持停用<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持港獨 唔好屈我"},{"pid":"45242cebb76a258dab3ed8560abc30ac66a37b5e","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebbddb761cd7cc4ed43a593cdbb55a35441ab9a1","tid":2211541,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b5875a8367b7f6fd5d7915629c0773aebf7775ca","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"當初會停用呢個字係因為1945年中華民國要求日本停用 <br />\n<br />\n不過到今日都支持停用<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持港獨 唔好屈我"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"我地叫嘅係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">共產黨嘅支那</span></span>而唔係<span class=\"xx-large\">國民黨嘅中國</span>"},{"pid":"e298b4458196ff10f675f9c59e31e1bb1b9f8bc3","tid":2211541,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45242cebb76a258dab3ed8560abc30ac66a37b5e","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebbddb761cd7cc4ed43a593cdbb55a35441ab9a1","tid":2211541,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b5875a8367b7f6fd5d7915629c0773aebf7775ca","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"當初會停用呢個字係因為1945年中華民國要求日本停用 <br />\n<br />\n不過到今日都支持停用<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持港獨 唔好屈我"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"我地叫嘅係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">共產黨嘅支那</span></span>而唔係<span class=\"xx-large\">國民黨嘅中國</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:32:20.000Z","msg":"明白 支持<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔係話特別鍾意國民黨 始終係列寧制式政黨 我比較希望聯省自治<br />\n<br />\n但佢睇呢個概念生不逢時 本來2010年時期係最好嘅機會 不過國際社會都顧住賴共賺錢 冇人聽當時喺Twitter 大陸人嘅勸告 所以今日西方社會面臨咁嘅困境係自己攞嚟<br />\n<br />\n我自己2015年嘅時候cap咗好多係支付上面討論民主制度起中國大陸地區落實嘅睇法 但唔知而家啲相仲喺唔喺度（嗰啲嘅回答就肯定全部刪除晒）"},{"pid":"6b08a2567435a4f0234d201c59bcee8e8b358593","tid":2211541,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45242cebb76a258dab3ed8560abc30ac66a37b5e","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebbddb761cd7cc4ed43a593cdbb55a35441ab9a1","tid":2211541,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b5875a8367b7f6fd5d7915629c0773aebf7775ca","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"當初會停用呢個字係因為1945年中華民國要求日本停用 <br />\n<br />\n不過到今日都支持停用<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持港獨 唔好屈我"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"我地叫嘅係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">共產黨嘅支那</span></span>而唔係<span class=\"xx-large\">國民黨嘅中國</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:34:47.000Z","msg":"仲有如果未來香港獨立我哋要比日本人同印度人非常好嘅待遇 我對呢個嘅做法係極保留 即使係所謂為印太地區着想<br />\n<br />\n就算做美國嘅細佬都唔應該完全咩都聽足美國支笛 如果唔係點會比佢哋覺得你好好恰 好似新加坡當年對嗰個食香口膠嘅美國人一樣打屎忽（我唔係支持佢呢啲戇居法例 我係講個背後嘅精神）"},{"pid":"cfa54e8b755915687d85a3f3a3ea1498e47eadef","tid":2211541,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e298b4458196ff10f675f9c59e31e1bb1b9f8bc3","tid":2